01:20:56.840 --> 01:21:02.840
Pet, štiri, tri, dve, ena.

01:21:07.319 --> 01:21:08.559
Ne morem.

01:21:08.560 --> 01:21:10.560
Vee, ne. Ne moreš …

01:21:14.520 --> 01:21:16.520
Jaz bom!

01:21:20.198 --> 01:21:21.358
Sranje.

01:21:21.359 --> 01:21:23.761
Napadli so nas in
blokirajo vse naše IP-je.

01:21:23.840 --> 01:21:25.840
Tommy, naredi nekaj!

01:21:31.118 --> 01:21:33.118
Ste me pogrešali?

01:21:35.439 --> 01:21:37.920
Začnimo izziv od začetka.

01:21:38.000 --> 01:21:39.759
Z nekom, ki je zares
pripravljen igrati.

01:21:39.760 --> 01:21:40.838
Ja!

01:21:40.840 --> 01:21:43.764
Ne delaj tega.
Ni vredno.

01:21:43.840 --> 01:21:46.363
Ustavita se!
Umaknita se!

01:21:47.078 --> 01:21:48.759
Zmešalo se ti je, lepotec.
Pridi nazaj!

01:21:48.760 --> 01:21:50.960
Je to res to, kar hočete?
Da se pobijemo med seboj?

01:21:51.000 --> 01:21:53.319
Ja!
–Seveda to hočete!

01:21:53.520 --> 01:21:55.278
Ubij ju!

01:21:55.279 --> 01:21:57.279
Mislite, da to zahteva pogum?

01:21:57.279 --> 01:22:01.001
Zakaj si ne odstranite mask
in pokažete svoje obraze?

01:22:01.078 --> 01:22:03.082
Ti. Odstrani masko.

01:22:03.158 --> 01:22:05.158
Kako ti je ime?

01:22:08.118 --> 01:22:11.090
Lahko je biti pogumen,
če si v množici.

01:22:11.158 --> 01:22:14.002
Če se skrivaš za
lažnim imenom.

01:22:14.078 --> 01:22:16.399
Se ne zavedate, da
ste odgovorni za vse,

01:22:16.479 --> 01:22:19.926
kar se zgodi danes,
tudi če samo gledate?

01:22:20.000 --> 01:22:22.765
O, mojbog,
res verjamete temu sranju?

01:22:22.840 --> 01:22:26.524
Igraj na zmago!

01:22:27.960 --> 01:22:31.567
Res hočete, da
eden izmed nas umre zaradi igre?

01:22:31.640 --> 01:22:34.881
Ja! Ja!

01:22:36.720 --> 01:22:38.720
Potem pa me ustreli!

01:22:40.399 --> 01:22:42.399
Izzivam te.

01:22:43.840 --> 01:22:45.840
V redu.

01:22:46.118 --> 01:22:48.118
Kdo hoče, da jo ustrelim?

01:22:48.118 --> 01:22:49.838
Vee, kaj se dogaja?

01:22:49.840 --> 01:22:52.729
Kdo hoče, da jo ustrelim?

01:22:52.800 --> 01:22:54.800
Tommy, kje je Vee?
–Pomirite se.

01:22:54.840 --> 01:22:56.438
Kakšna igra je to?
Hočem odgovor!

01:22:56.439 --> 01:22:57.559
Kaj počnete?

01:22:57.560 --> 01:22:59.720
Bolje, da mi poveste,
drugače kličem policijo!

01:22:59.800 --> 01:23:01.478
Ne, ne policije!
–Nancy, pomirite se.

01:23:01.479 --> 01:23:03.157
Hočete, da jo ustrelim?

01:23:03.158 --> 01:23:05.729
Ubij jo!
–Glasujte za!

01:23:05.800 --> 01:23:09.282
Glasujte za, če hočete,
da jo ubijem!

01:23:09.359 --> 01:23:11.966
Ne glasujte za, glasujte proti!
–Hočete, da jo ubijem?

01:23:12.037 --> 01:23:14.122
Hočete, da jo ubijem?

01:23:15.399 --> 01:23:17.640
Dajte no! Glasujte proti!

01:23:19.158 --> 01:23:21.765
Glasujte proti!

01:23:21.840 --> 01:23:25.447
Ti. Glasuj za, glasuj za!

01:23:42.520 --> 01:23:44.520
Dajte mi vedeti, da to hočete!

01:23:48.600 --> 01:23:52.524
Imejmo malce anarhije.

01:23:52.600 --> 01:23:56.444
Uspeva nam. IP-ji
sedaj prihajajo hitreje.

01:23:56.520 --> 01:23:57.878
Vee! Iti morava! Zdaj!

01:23:57.880 --> 01:23:59.157
O, mojbog!

01:23:59.158 --> 01:24:01.367
Družba, nadaljujmo!

01:24:09.037 --> 01:24:11.037
O, mojbog! Vee!

01:24:18.760 --> 01:24:20.886
Vee!

01:24:20.960 --> 01:24:22.960
Ne! Ne! Ne!

01:24:24.399 --> 01:24:26.402
Poglej me, Vee!

01:24:04.538 --> 01:24:08.590
<i>Naj ustreli Vee?
–Ja.</i>

01:24:42.015 --> 01:24:44.015
<i>Kyle P. Ramos.
Pripomogel si k umoru.</i>

01:24:47.359 --> 01:24:49.359
<i>Nico Stone.
Pripomogel si k umoru.</i>

01:24:52.698 --> 01:24:54.698
<i>Craig Griffin.
Pripomogel si k umoru.</i>

01:24:57.189 --> 01:24:59.189
<i>Caroline Morgan.
Pripomogla si k umoru.</i>

01:24:59.319 --> 01:25:01.345
<i>Se želiš izpisati?
V redu.</i>

01:25:01.400 --> 01:25:03.900
To je moje pravo ime.

01:25:46.359 --> 01:25:47.559
Počakaj! Stoj!

01:25:47.560 --> 01:25:48.918
Mojbog!

01:25:48.920 --> 01:25:50.519
V redu je! V redu je!

01:25:50.520 --> 01:25:53.524
Stoj! V redu je! V redu sem.

01:25:54.640 --> 01:25:56.640
O, mojbog!

01:25:56.760 --> 01:25:58.760
Oprosti.

01:26:00.960 --> 01:26:02.878
Sodeloval si pri tem?

01:26:02.880 --> 01:26:05.884
Načrt je bil njen.
Poklicala me je Sydney.

01:26:05.960 --> 01:26:07.478
Zato sem tu.

01:26:07.479 --> 01:26:08.838
Ampak pištola …

01:26:08.840 --> 01:26:10.840
Slepi naboji.

01:26:15.439 --> 01:26:17.439
Ni prava.

01:26:18.880 --> 01:26:20.880
O, mojbog!

01:26:24.118 --> 01:26:26.645
Prestrašil si me.

01:26:28.000 --> 01:26:30.000
Sva v redu?

01:26:30.760 --> 01:26:33.238
Ja. Svobodni smo.

01:26:33.319 --> 01:26:36.323
Huda je. Pazi nanjo.

01:26:37.979 --> 01:26:39.117
<i>Izpiši se.</i>

01:26:39.118 --> 01:26:41.176
To je to. Zadnji igralec se je izpisal.
–Nam je uspelo?

01:26:41.198 --> 01:26:42.599
Nobenega več ni!
Igra se sesuva!

01:26:42.600 --> 01:26:46.810
Smo?
–Nerve je uradno izključen!

01:26:46.880 --> 01:26:48.880
Izigrali smo igro.

01:26:48.920 --> 01:26:52.479
Vi ste najbolj neumni
pametni otroci, ki jih poznam.

01:26:53.760 --> 01:26:55.760
Žal mi je.
–Ne, meni je.

01:26:55.760 --> 01:26:59.207
Žal mi je, da sem
te potegnil v to.

01:27:00.640 --> 01:27:04.042
Želim si, da bi se
lahko spoznala drugače.

01:27:04.720 --> 01:27:06.720
Jaz si ne.

01:27:07.399 --> 01:27:09.237
Stari!

01:27:09.238 --> 01:27:11.238
Ti.

01:27:11.640 --> 01:27:13.640
Kakšna zvezda!

01:27:14.319 --> 01:27:16.448
Izgleda, da vam lahko
vrnem ves denar.

01:27:16.520 --> 01:27:18.398
Ne kličejo me Hekerka
Kween kar tako.

01:27:18.399 --> 01:27:20.560
Res? Hvala.
–Ja.

01:27:31.920 --> 01:27:36.243
Nor prvi zmenek, kajne?
–To je bil zmenek?

01:27:38.760 --> 01:27:43.368
Mimogrede, moje pravo
ime je Sam.

01:27:47.600 --> 01:27:51.082
Lepo te je bilo spoznati, Sam.

01:27:52.439 --> 01:27:54.600
Lepo te je bilo spoznati, Vee.

01:28:21.903 --> 01:28:25.047
Hej, Vee.
V New Yorku je 28 stopinj!

